      "span_text": "On the contrary, it is easy to show that the penalty will depend on the cost of capital and is decreasing in this parameter if we assume that (i) the protection buyer could credibly commit ex-ante to retain the equity tranche risk and that, ex-post, this is incentive compatible or (ii) credit derivatives are public contracts. [CITATION_1]"
